ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Graduate research is intensive, satisfying, and interesting. Would recommend.
This course is all about research. As this is a required component for a PhD, I would recommend this course to another student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: My knowledge of chemistry and lab practices has increased exponentially since I started. I learn new techniques almost every day and I foresee this continuing for a long time.
This course provides hands-on experience in organic chemistry. It is the course that is providing the most significant contribution to the completion of my degree.
